Description:
    Generate boilerplate files to get you up and running with stimulus_reflex

Example:
    rails generate stimulus_reflex example

    This will create
        app/javascript/controllers/application_controller.js
        app/javascript/controllers/example_controller.js
        app/reflexes/application_reflex.rb
        app/reflexes/example_reflex.rb

    rails generate stimulus_reflex:controller example

    This will create:
        app/javascript/controllers/application_controller.js (if it does not already exist)
        app/javascript/controllers/example_controller.js

    rails generate stimulus_reflex:reflex example

    This will create:
        app/reflexes/application_reflex.rb (if it does not already exist)
        app/reflexes/example_reflex.rb
